         <h1 class="article-title uppercase">
          Mila Kunis and Ashton Kutcher Welcome First Child Together
         </h1>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="post-text p402_premium">
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 author-panel">
         <a href="http://www.her.ie/author/rebecca-mcknight/5">
          <img class="avatar author-image img-circle" nopin="no-pin" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/0684c2e642e5376d4863e34e12671699.jpg?s=100&amp;d=mm"/>
         </a>
         <a class="author-name" href="http://www.her.ie/author/rebecca-mcknight/5">
          By
          <strong>
           Rebecca McKnight
          </strong>
         </a>
         <div class="clearfix">
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-9 col-sm-12 col-sm-12 post-body">
         <div class="post-content">
          <p>
           <b>
            Mila Kunis and Ashton Kutcher have reportedly welcomed their first child together.
           </b>
          </p>
          <p>
           According to a number of sources, the star coupleare now the proud parents of a baby girl.The 31-year-old actress gave birth at Cedars-Sinai hospital in Los Angeles after arriving there shortly after 6am this morning,
          </p>
          <p>
           According to TMZ, Mila and Ashton
           <b>
           </b>
           arrived by themselves to the hospital with no entourage in tow.No other information about the little girls name or birth weight has been released.
          </p>
          <p>
           Mila and Ashton got
           <a href="http://www.her.ie/celeb/mila-kunis-and-ashton-kutcher-are-engaged/" target="_blank">
            engaged earlier this year
           </a>
           having been together since 2011. They have known each other for years and worked together on
           <i>
            That 70s Show
           </i>
           .
          </p>
          <p>
           Speaking previously about the birth, the
           <em>
            Black Swan
           </em>
           actress revealed:Two people are allowed in my delivery room. My doctor and my significant other. And he is staying above the action. Hell be head to head... Unless he wants to risk his life and see.
          </p>
          <p>
           <img alt="Chicago Bears v Pittsbugh Steelers" src="http://m0.her.ie/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/mila-ashton-2.jpg"/>
           <br/>
           <em>
            Ashton and Mila have been dating since 2011.
           </em>
          </p>
         </div>
